s hourly wage from  to  and cut skilled trade wages  per hour the strike cost general motors  billion as the automaker lost the production of its chevrolet malibu sedan and other vehicles productsedit key products include axles drive shafts front axle universal joints and sealing and thermalmanagement products axlesedit  corporate  bolt differential saginaw inch axle demolitionedit after closing its factories in detroit in  american axle and manufacturing had started a demolition project in late  much of the old manufacturing facility had been demolished by bulldozers and cranes also in february  it was reported and confirmed that most of the detroithamtramck manufacturing site had been sold  to a californiabased industrial realty group irg llc who specialize in the use of industrial buildings for other developments such as apartment complexes in  american axle continued to own its headquarters and greenbelt property at the site it planned to build an engineering facility in the sole building left standing from the original manufacturing complex us competitorsedit meritor dana referencesedit  a b c d e american axle  manufacturing  annual report form k filing date feb   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved july     joes union review american axle strike joes union review blogger retrieved  april   gm to slash expenses raise cash to move forward auto trends retrieved  july   american axle sells detroit manufacturing complex to industrial realty group the detroit news burden melissa retrieved  february  external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleamericanaxleoldid categories auto parts suppliers of the united statesmanufacturing companies based in detroitmanufacturing companies established in  establishments in michiganprivate equity portfolio companiesblackstone group companiescompanies listed on the new york stock exchangehidden categories pages using deprecated image syntax navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontribution