 sales the company hopes to reduce the percentage of total sales made to gm below  by in addition sales to customers other than gm during the fiscal year ended december   increased  over the previous year to usd  million setting a new record for the company   competitors dana gkn linamar magna meritor zf if you would like to see more please register for a free trial nonbinding and without any initial or follow up costs after registering a free trial account you will also gain access to who supplies whom information the latest development trends and much more register here headquartered in tokyo marklines is a japanese company listed on the jasdaq stock exchange the marklines automotive industry portal provides vehicle production and sales information technology reports part supplier insights for almost  suppliers and much more for companies around the world additionally marklines provides an online service for oems and suppliers to promote their products more than  automotive industry companies from all levels of the supply chain including oems parts makers and material suppliers are currently subscribed to marklines service shareholders listed on new york stock exchange products driveline systems rear beam axlesrear axle systemsfront axlesdriveshaftsmultipiece driveshaftstracrite axle differentialstorque transfer devices  electronic control couplingsconstant velocity jointsdrivetrain systems transfer cases power transfer unitstracrite transaxles  transfer case differentialspowertrain components transmissions  transfer case components intake manifolds oil pans bell housingschassis system componentsiride suspension modulessmartbar electronic stabilizer systemssubframe cradleupperlower control armsattaching bushinghardwaremetal formed productsaxle shaftsinput shaftsoutput shaftsdifferential gearstrunnions and spidersfront  rear hypoid pinionshypoid ring gearsfront axle disconnect componentsinner and outer tie rods and relay rodsnet formed gearsnet formed splinesclutch